<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>认知与思考 on 知行社</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/categories/%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E4%B8%8E%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83/</link><description>Recent content in 认知与思考 on 知行社</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/categories/%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E4%B8%8E%E6%80%9D%E8%80%83/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>为什么很多老板学AI，最后学成了信息焦虑</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/why-bosses-learn-ai-become-anxious/</link><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/why-bosses-learn-ai-become-anxious/</guid><description>花了半年时间学AI，结果反而更焦虑？问题不在于你学得不够多，而在于你学错了方向。这篇文章帮你找到真正的卡点。</description></item><item><title>用AI的人，正在悄悄变笨</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/ai-making-people-dumb/</link><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/ai-making-people-dumb/</guid><description>AI帮你写代码、写报告、导航出行，效率翻倍。但有一件事没人告诉你：用久了，那块肌肉会悄悄萎缩。</description></item><item><title>AI帮你到了终点，但路上的风景只能自己看</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/helicopter-era-ai-cant-replace-experience/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/helicopter-era-ai-cant-replace-experience/</guid><description>Vibe Coding时代，AI能帮你写代码、整理数据、生成方案，但判断力只能自己踩坑练出来。从儿子考试焦虑到程序员白板死磕，说的是同一件事：没走过的路，不算你走过。</description></item><item><title>别解释了，点亮「他」</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/stop-explaining-just-show-ai/</link><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/stop-explaining-just-show-ai/</guid><description>跟身边人聊AI总没反应？不是他们不聪明，是你讲错了。一个FMCG从业者怎么让周围人真正相信AI能改变工作——不靠解释，靠让他们看见。</description></item></channel></rss>